text.tspan: │ Function │ NULL Input │ Empty Set │ Example │
│ SUM(col) │ Skips NULL │ Returns NULL │ empty → NULL│
│ AVG(col) │ Skips NULL │ Returns NULL │ empty → NULL│
│ MIN(col) │ Skips NULL │ Returns NULL │ empty → NULL│
│ MAX(col) │ Skips NULL │ Returns NULL │ empty → NULL│
• COUNT(*) is unique: counts rows regardless of NULL
• All other aggregates skip NULL values
• SUM/AVG/MIN/MAX return NULL for empty sets
• COUNT returns 0 for empty sets (never NULL)
